  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dbb \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dca\u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dba\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0da9\u0dcf \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The egg industry also collapses",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The egg producers of Paduvasnuwara area say that they are facing severe difficulties due to not being able to sell eggs.",
        "They said that the eggs produced for many days are kept in the farms like this.",
        "Lack of ability to transport eggs due to the ongoing fuel crisis is the main reason for this problem.",
        "Eggs are a perishable food and should be consumed within a few days.",
        "About sixty percent of the eggs required by the country are produced in the Paduvasnuwara area.",
        "The farm owners say that the distribution of eggs should be done on a daily basis, but it is not possible to do the distribution several times a day.",
        "They also say that even a single vehicle that transported eggs across the country does not come to the farms to take the eggs.",
        "It has been a difficult task for the farm owners to provide a proper nutritious diet and the farm owners said that egg production has decreased.",
        "Even though they are running the farm to maintain the industry, they have to suffer losses on a daily basis.",
        "As of today, seventy-five percent of the egg production industry in the area has left.",
        "The industrialists say that they have no ability to continue the industry in the face of the economic crisis in the country.",
        "They also emphasize that the government has a responsibility to prepare a program to protect local industries at a time when the country is bankrupt and unable to import food and goods."
      ],
